headline.main: Our Washington Correspondence.; THE HOUSE FROM THE GALLERY--THE SOUTHERN CAUCUS--THE VOTE FOR HAMILTON--PRIVILEGES OF REPORTERS AND CORRESPONDENTS, ETC., ETC.

docs.lead_paragraph: After an absence of a fortnight, I find the House of Representatives in much the same state as it stood on Christmas Eve--with the difference, perhaps, that the uncombined National elements have become more obstinate in the resolve to demand supremacy for their several organizations.

docs.snippet: Thirty members answered to their names in the Senate last evening, and a quorum was present in the House.

headline.main: FROM JAMAICA.; Legislative Proceedings Immigration Need ed The American Divers Trade, &c.

docs.lead_paragraph: The Royal Mail Steamer Teviot, with the London mails of the 17th of November, arrived at this port yesterday morning! She brings intelligence that the Queen has conferred the dignity of Knighthood upon BRYAN EDWARDS, Esq., Chief-Justice of Jamaica. Mr. EDWARDS is the son of the celebrated historian of the West Indies.

docs.lead_paragraph: THE WEATHER AND THE STREETS. On Saturday the mercury in the thermometer rose and the rain in the evening descended in torrents. The storm passed away with the night, and Sunday and Monday were like days in June. But such walking! Mud to the right of you; mud to the left of you; mud in front of you; wherever you rambled. No lady ventured forth without her Balmoral.
